ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/hostus.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\"></a></p><p>Andrew from HostUS just sent over this offer and we\u2019re happy to be able to feature them once again as they were ranked #6 on the LowEndTalk Best Provider Poll in 2016!</p><p>HostUS is a registered company in Delaware, USA (#&nbsp;5491145), their WHOIS is public, and you can find their <a href=\"https://hostus.us/terms-and-conditions.html\" target=\"_blank\">ToS/legal documents here.</a></p><p>They accept&nbsp;PayPal, Bitcoin, Credit Card and Skrill, as well as all major bank cards (AMEX, Discover, MasterCard, VISA).</p><p><strong>In their own words:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><em>\u201cHostUS was founded in 2012 with our first location in Atlanta, GA. We had since grown to 9 global locations. Throughout the years HostUS has grown from a small start-up to its existing state. In the USA and Europe we operate our own ASNs (AS7489 / AS25926) and our own hardware. In Asia Pacific (Hong Kong, Sydney and Singapore) we partner with SoftLayer (AS36351). We use direct allocated IP addresses in most of our locations.\u201d</em></p><p><strong>Special OpenVZ Plans:</strong></p><p>Container-based OpenVZ virtualization for running your favourite Linux distribution without the kernel overhead or management complexity. OpenVZ services are available in all nine of HostUS\u2019s worldwide locations. The following plans are available in the new Amsterdam location as well as all our USA / Europe locations.</p><div></div><div>Available OpenVZ OSes can be <a href=\"https://my.hostus.us/knowledgebase.php?action=displayarticle&amp;id=82\" target=\"_blank\">found here</a>.</div><p><strong>Here are the offers:</strong></p><table style=\"height: 265px\" width=\"650\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>US/EU Special 1</strong><p></p><ul><li>6GB RAM</li><li>6GB vSwap</li><li>4 vCPU Cores (Fair Share)</li><li>150GB Disk Space</li><li>5TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>6x IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ / Breeze Control Panel</li><li>$18/quarter</li><li>$65/year</li><li>[<a href=\"https://my.hostus.us/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=202\">Order Now</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>US/EU Special 2</strong><p></p><ul><li>768MB RAM</li><li>768MB vSwap</li><li>1 vCPU Core (Fair Share)</li><li>20GB Disk Space</li><li>2TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>4x IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ / Breeze Control Panel</li><li>$16/year</li><li>[<a href=\"https://my.hostus.us/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=201\">Order Now</a>]</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><div></div><p><strong>Additional Offers:</strong></p><p><span id=\"more-10677\"></span></p><div></div><div><strong>Special KVM VPS Plans:</strong></div><div></div><div>Full KVM virtualization ready to run nearly any operating system (no module incompatibility and bothering support to enable modules). Run the latest Linux kernel, run BSD, run Docker. Choose from already built templates or manual ISO installs. All KVM VPS plans include three snapshots which you can create and restore at any time.</div><p></p><div>Available KVM OSes can be <a href=\"https://my.hostus.us/knowledgebase.php?action=displayarticle&amp;id=101\" target=\"_blank\">found here</a>.</div><p></p><div>KVM locations available: Los Angeles, Atlanta, Washington DC, London.</div><p></p><div>Note: The coupon <u>LEBKVM30</u> can be used on all KVM plans starting from KVM-1, <a href=\"https://hostus.us/kvm-vps.html\" target=\"_blank\">listed here</a>.</div><p></p><div></div><table style=\"height: 265px\" width=\"650\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>KVM-1</strong><p></p><ul><li>1GB RAM</li><li>2x vCPU</li><li>45GB HDD</li><li>1TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>1x IPv6</li><li>KVM / Breeze Control Panel</li><li>Coupon: LEBKVM30</li><li>$5.57</li><li>[<a href=\"https://my.hostus.us/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=308\">Order Now</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>KVM-2</strong><p></p><ul><ul><li>2GB RAM</li><li>2x vCPU</li><li>75GB HDD</li><li>2TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>1x IPv6</li><li>KVM / Breeze Control Panel</li><li>Coupon: LEBKVM30</li><li>$9.77/month</li><li>[<a href=\"https://my.hostus.us/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=309\">Order Now</a>]</li></ul></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>Network Info &amp; Hardware\u2014&gt;</strong></p><p>Please see <a href=\"https://hostus.us/network.html\" target=\"_blank\">here</a> for full network information.</p><div>\u2013 Intel Xeon CPUs (exact model depending on location / virtualization)</div><div>\u2013 At least 64GB DDR3 or DDR4</div><div>\u2013 Minimum 4 HDD / SSD-Cached RAID 10</div><div>\u2013 1Gbps uplink</div><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fhostus-new-ams-location-exclusive-kvm-promotion%2F&amp;t=HostUS%20-%20New%20AMS%20Location%20%26amp%3B%20Exclusive%20KVM%20Promotion\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=HostUS%20-%20New%20AMS%20Location%20%26amp%3B%20Exclusive%20KVM%20Promotion&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fhostus-new-ams-location-exclusive-kvm-promotion%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-